Movie.Name: Transformers: Rise of the Beasts
Movie.About: Transformers: Rise of the Beasts will take audiences on a `90s globetrotting adventure and introduce the Maximals, Predacons, and Terrorcons to the existing battle on earth between Autobots and Decepticons.

Movie.Name: Por Thozhil
Movie.About: An academically bright but faint-hearted cop needs to overcome his fears in order to succeed. He must team up with a hostile and a reclusive senior cop to catch a serial killer on the loose.

Movie.Name: Veeran
Movie.About: Kumaran, a 15-year-old boy living in Veeranor, gets struck by lightning and goes into a short coma. After recovery, he gradually realizes that he has superpowers of lightning and mind control.
